##TICKET 1 — Product Search Functionality

#ID: NOP-SEARCH-001
Title: Verify product search returns relevant results
Steps:
1.	Use search bar 
2.	Search for “book” or “computer” 
Expected Result:
-Relevant products displayed 
-No unrelated items shown

**Actual Result (Book):**
Search shows products (laptops) titled ‘mackbook’, ‘ultrabook’, ‘sleekbook’. Search included specific word searched with search bar in product as result of search.

**Actual Result (Computer):**
Search shows product (service) titled ‘Build your own computer’. Search included specific word searched with search bar in product as result of search.


**Status:**
Pass
Notes:
Search bar shows products (laptops or service) with specific word in name or title, not product classification (books or computers) which may be confusing to user as user might be looking for product (books or computers) and receive search results with search word in the name or title.


